Of course, everyone is entitled to their opinion, but that doesn’t shield it from criticism either.

I mean if anyone considers this their GOTY, more power to you, but I just find it very difficult to justify it being crowned GOTY over the likes of Bloodstained, FE Three Houses, DMC5, REmake 2 and Sekiro. Or even another short indie game like Katana ZERO.

Both this and The Lighthouse being majorly snubbed from the Oscars is why I don’t take awards shows seriously. UGG is a fun game by all means, but I doubt anyone would say it outclasses every other game that dropped last year unless it was all they played.
